storyInfo: Lava attempts to manage her attitude towards Hibiscus, but fails in the end. Provoked by Cuora, she looks to apologize to her sister, but is beaten to the punch by a letter from Hibiscus.

attributes.content: 11:10 A.M. \ Clear
Rhodes Island Landship, Cabin No. 2, Operator Living Area
Breathe in—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: —Breathe out.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Empty your mind. Purge your thoughts.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Phew...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Alright. No problems.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Heart rate unaccelerated, emotions holding steady. You're alright, Lava. You can do this!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: This is the one! You're gonna talk to Hibiscus without getting pissed at her!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, Lava~! You're just in time!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I've prepared you a healthy meal for today too, so make sure you eat it!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: What? For hell's sakes, who'd want to eat your 'healthy meals' day in day out?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ...Hfff...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (No, no, Lava. Don't talk to her like this.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Patience. Bring out your will of a master fortune-teller, and control yourself...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Steady heart. Steady heart.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Phew.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Uh, no, I mean...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: With every day being healthy meals, I'm a little tired... I'm not saying I'm fed up with you! Don't overthink it!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Haha, what's all that rubbish for? Of course I know you wouldn't be fed up with your sister~
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Come on, this is today's lunch. Make sure you don't leave a single scrap!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: It's been getting cold lately. Balanced nutrition is the number one defense against getting ill, don't you know?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: Blugh...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hmm? What's wrong?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I've told... I'm TELLING you...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Forget this fff... flavor for a moment. You know the thing I hate eating most is tomatoes, right?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Uh-huh. Why wouldn't I know?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: So why...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: —Why would you go and stuff all this boiled tomato into MY lunch!?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Aw, don't get worked up. It's because tomatoes are very nutritious, of course~
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: And don't think I didn't know! Don't you always sneak any food you don't like onto Kroos's plate?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: And not just that, you've only been eating meat recently, without a single vegetable in sight, haven't you?
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: You can't be like that, you can't be picky! 'Bad kids' like you who don't listen are in need of a little stricter punishment!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: I'll be watching you to make sure you eat every last bite today!
attributes.name: Hibiscus

attributes.content: (Deep breath)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Don't get angry don't get angry don't get angry.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Don't get... aaaarrrghh fffor gods' sakes I can't do it I can't take this!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Can you stop being like this ever! Don't treat me! Like! A child—!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ugh...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And it all ends up like this once again.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I didn't want to argue with her, but she's just too annoying, isn't she? Who forces people to eat what they hate like that? Urp... I still feel like I want to throw up a little.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ugh.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Whatever. It's my fault in the end for not controlling my temper...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What what what? Who's bullying you?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Tell me quick, I'll beat them up! Just watch me pummel any rotten bully into next week! Just liiiiiiike—this!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Waagh!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Stop swinging your bat around in here! That's dangerous as hell!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hold on, didn't the Doctor say hitting people with your bat was forbidden on the ship? Wasn't writing a whole letter enough to learn anything?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, right! Awgh... I hate writing self reflection letters! I don't wanna write any more!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Oh well, that's okay, I can do it without using my bat. Look, I can smash my backpack into any baddies! My backpack's really useful! Amiya and the bosses said I was really cool and strong!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: So don't worry, Lava, it's my turn to make the baddies learn!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: I don't worry about... look, just pause, calm down for now. Mind you don't get dragged in for another lecture.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And nobody's bullying me.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Really?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Really.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Staring)
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You're lying!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Wha?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: If nobody's bullying you, then why do you look like you're having a really sad time, Lava?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Sad? Do... do I?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No way, you're seeing me wrong! I don't—
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Of course you do! I don't see things wrong!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Your eyebrows are all crumpled like that one time you were playing piano and the lid smashed into your hands! You look like you're really hurt!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You're blowing this out of proportion!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Am I right or not!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Ugh.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Fine, okay, you're right. But it's not anything that serious. *sigh* I just had an argument with that stupid Hibiscus, nothing unusual...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, is it a Hibiscus thing again?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Awwww. If it's a Hibiscus thing, then I can't help you out...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Why not?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Because Hibiscus isn't a baddie, right? She was really nice and gentle last time she examined me, and she gave me a little cake too! It was super tasty!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Hmph. That's just like her, playing nice.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What's so amazing about cakes? It's not like I can't make them...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And with HER abilities, baking something that counts as edible these days? Do you have any idea how many times she had to fail before that?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And she couldn't throw away anything she'd ruined, and she forced me to clean up her awful messes for her.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Um... um? I don't get it!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Does that mean you got a lot of cakes to eat?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: As if it'd mean that!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ugh... forget it. I don't know what I'm doing telling you this.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Basically, if you actually had a brother or sister or whatever, you'd understand what kinds of maddening creatures big sisters are! Especially the oppressive, dictatorial ones like Hibiscus...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hey. What's the silence for?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Um. How do I put this?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I think, it's really nice!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Huh? What part of that's nice?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's really nice, the idea of having a sibling... I really wanna experience it.
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: I could ask the Doctor to be my brother or sister or something, but, it wouldn't be like it is between you and Hibiscus, right?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Uh, that'd be, I guess... not the same?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Knew it...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Then, Lava.
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: What.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I thought of a good idea—you just gotta make Hibiscus be my older sister!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Pfff—!!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: *cough*, *cough* *cough* *cough*... Wh—What kind of insane idea is that?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'm not being insane, I'm saying it very seriously!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Do you understand that, like, sisters... familial sisters are blood-related? They—Even if you wanted to, they're not something you can just give up to other people!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Whaaa—what does that matter? I don't care if there's no blood or whatever, right?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You still can't!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Can't I really? Pleaaaase—
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You're always saying Hibiscus is your sworn nemesis, and she's the incarnation of evil thingies, right? So if you don't want your big sister, you can just let me have her!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: That—I...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No. In one word, no!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Why not?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: There isn't a why not! No just means no!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Spoilsport!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Say whatever you want!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I don't get it. Whyyy...? Okay...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: But for super real, then, why are you always fighting with Hibiscus, then?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: I heard from Fang that when you just joined the squad, and you first saw Hibiscus, you almost said you were gonna quit right there. Is that true?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: What's Fang doing telling you all that...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: So it's real?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: It's real.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh... but that's really weird, 'cause why didn't you know Hibiscus was gonna be in your squad too? Um, didn't you come to Rhodes Island together?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: What are you asking for? Where'd all this curiosity of yours come from?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Tell me, tell me!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Don't—Don't shake me... Fine, fine, if I tell you you'll be happy, right? This is doing my head in, but there's not even much to hide anyway.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hibiscus and I did leave home together at first. However, midway, something unexpected occurred...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: As in—*ahem*—I had an argument with her halfway along, so we split up.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: That's not unexpected at all!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Shut up! I know it's not cool at all either!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It was an argument about—uh—I can't remember what it was, forget it... essentially, after we argued I was pissed beyond belief, and ran off to vent some steam, and ended up going a little too far without realizing...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I wasn't too good with telling apart wasteland geography, and I went off any sort of signed road while I was still fuming, so I... just...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Wait, no way? You ran too far away and got lost just like that? Alone in the wasteland?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: More or less. Luckily I came across a caravan afterwards, and they took me up close to Leithanien.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Lava, you...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You're a huge little dummy—!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Huh?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You're a dummy! You're a huge little dummy! How can anyone get so lost they go from Victoria to Leithanien? Ahahahaha—
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You're the literal last person I want to hear this from!!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: But my fortune telling didn't miss. It was my fated encounter!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: If I hadn't followed the caravan for Leithanien, I would've never met my teacher, and if he never taught me music, then I'd definitely be having a hard time learning Originium Arts now!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh, that's true. You learn Originium Arts really good and fast too...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: The instructors and Pith all say you're great. And the elite operator sir I saw last mission, with the stiff face and the eyes like this, and the weirdly nice voice, he said so too!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Actually, you've been going to the training grounds every day. Is that because you're learning from that operator guy?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Tch. I'd like to be, but when would something that good ever happen?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: How would someone as important as Master Logos ever have the time to teach me specifically? Just the couple of words he gave last time are already amazing enough...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And what was with your description of him just now?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Don't cock your head and play dumb! He's a master, a cool and strong and eye-catching graceful mysterious composed master! You need to have a little more respect towards him!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Wow... I got it, I got it~
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You really worship that elite operator sir guy, huh...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: It's not worship, it's respect! Respect for the strong!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hmph. There'll be a day when I become just as strong as him!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Uh, huuuh...
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: (But the look on Lava's face is totally like when all the nice people out at that logistics office last time saw Sora singing...)
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: (Ohh, now I get it! So this is what respect is!)
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: But, you know, I still feel really sorry.
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Sorry for what?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Umm... I was thinking, see, if Hibiscus became my big sister, then you'd start calling me a big sister too.
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Sorry!
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You can dream on! Like hell I would!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And obviously me and Hibiscus are the exact same age! Why's she the big sister and I'm the little one?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Let me make it clear, I'm literally taller than the both of you!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: It's nothing to do with height. Hibiscus is really caring of me, so she's a big sister to me. But I always feel like you're younger than me.
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: I can't make heads or tails of what you're saying... You mean I don't care for you?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Awwwwaawa stop puwwing on my face—
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Hmph. Someone should've taught you this sooner or later.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Remember! Never judge a book by its cover, and especially not when you're in front of a Sarkaz! For a Sarkaz, age and appearance are two separate matters!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Oh! Are you actually like the kind of old lady that looks young instead? Just like Dr. Warfarin?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Not quite.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: You aren't?
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: Whatever. I shouldn't be talking to you about this.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Actually, don't tell Dr. Warfarin what you just said under any circumstances either. You will 100% be killed.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Let's leave it at that. I still have some things to do, so I'll be heading off.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Ah! Where are you gonna go play, Lava? I wanna come with—
attributes.name: Cuora

attributes.content: You—are—not! I'm not off to play, and don't you follow me!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: I'm going to deal with a few matters...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: No-one's in.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Weird. How late is it? Hibiscus should've come back at this time already...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Honestly. It's all that Cuora's fault with all the weird stuff she spouted.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: ('Let me have your sister.' In what universe? She's not a commodity. How would anyone ever...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Spoilsport, my ass. If we really could switch and she'd stop being my sister, I'd thank every star in the whole goddamn sky! It's not like I have any choice when it comes to sibling stuff...)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (...For—Forget it.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (I shouldn't have lost my temper over today. Being wrong is being wrong. Nothing I can't recognize there.)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (When Hibiscus gets back, I'll apologize to her—)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: What is this... Cake—and... a letter?
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.text: To Lava: Your sister's looking after patients in the Medical Department tonight and probably can't make it back, so don't wait for me in the evening! I heard from Instructor Dobermann that you've been really hardworking lately, always paying special attention to practicing your Originium Arts, right? A couple of Caster operators including Pith and that Logos were all complimenting you, saying you've got a natural gift, and you learn extraordinarily well! As your big sister, seeing you so outstanding makes me feel very, truly happy. The only thing is, your sister's a doctor, and from a doctor's perspective, things can also make me worry.

Recently, you've been waking up very early every morning to practice, right? When you stay in the training rooms all morning, sometimes you even forget to eat breakfast, and you rush through your lunch and dinner, your diet is imbalanced. And both as a doctor and your big sister, it's very hard not to feel uneasy about it. Frequent casting of Originium Arts is going to have some effect or other on our conditions, and if we're not careful, the risk will balloon. I know a lot of effort is a good thing, but you need to take care, too. You can't ever neglect your body's health.

What happened at lunch today was your sister's fault. I shouldn't have acted so obstinate while knowing full well you don't like tomatoes. I'm really sorry, Lava. Recently, you've actually been trying to get along with me better, right? That makes me very happy. So, I'll reflect properly on myself too, and strive not to make you upset next time! The cake on the table is a gift of apology. If you can forgive your big sister, go on and give it a taste. I've been secretly practicing for a while by myself, and baked this one specially for you. I'm sure it'll be something you like!

attributes.content: What is she—writing something so—so sympathetic for? Doesn't she get embarrassed?!
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: She really is an evil one... just too evil...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: She even apologized first before I could. That's not cool at all...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: (Takes a big bite of the cake)
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Blugh. She put something weird inside it yet again.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And she said she was sure I'd like it... hmph. It's not even sweet enough. Disqualified.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: And wouldn't she forget to eat, spending all night busy at Medical? And she tells me I don't take care of my health. She's exactly the same.
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Fine, then. In exchange for the cake, I'll need to force myself to go give her something to eat...
attributes.name: Lava

attributes.content: Heh. You really are hopeless without me, aren't you, you huge dummy sister.
attributes.name: Lava
